OL,3,CHeseltine: Victory over striking
OL,4,Cminers 'benefited communities'
OL,6,FLord Heseltine has said the
OL,7,Fgovernment's victory over striking
OL,8,Fminers in the 1980s brought "great
OL,9,Fbenefit" to pit communities.
OL,11,FToday, 5 March, marks 40 years since
OL,12,Fminers at Cortonwood Colliery in South
OL,13,FYorkshire walked out in what signalled
OL,14,Fthe start of one of the most
OL,15,Facrimonious industrial disputes in
OL,16,FBritish history.
