OL,6,FThe strikes saw about three quarters
OL,7,Fof the country's 187,000 miners walk
OL,8,Fout in protest.
OL,10,FThe dispute lasted a year, before
OL,11,Fminers agreed to return to work in
OL,12,FMarch 1985.
OL,14,FLord Heseltine said the Conservatives
OL,15,Fgovernment had inherited problems left
OL,16,Fby the previous Labour administration.
