OL,3,CHeseltine: Victory over striking
OL,4,Cminers 'benefited communities'
OL,6,F"The issue was not a new one, it was
OL,7,Fan old one, which had undermined the
OL,8,FBritish economy for decades, we had to
OL,9,Fdeal with it and we had to bring the
OL,10,Funions within the law of the land.
OL,11,FThat was the issue and there was no
OL,12,Fdoubt in our minds of what we had to
OL,13,Fdo."
OL,15,FAt times there were violent clashes
OL,16,Fbetween those on the picket lines and
OL,17,Fthe police drafted in to manage the
OL,18,Fstrikes, including during the
OL,19,Fnotorious Battle of Orgreave in
OL,20,FRotherham, on 18 June 1984.
