OL,6,FNinety-three people were arrested.
OL,7,FMany are still trying to clear their
OL,8,Fname.
OL,10,FLord Heseltine said police had "little
OL,11,Fchoice".
OL,13,F"You've got to ask what the pickets
OL,14,Fwere doing and what techniques they
OL,15,Fused, and the violence they used to
OL,16,Fstop other miners who wanted to work
OL,17,Ffrom doing so," he said.
