OL,3,CHeseltine: Victory over striking
OL,4,Cminers 'benefited communities'
OL,6,FThe miners' ultimate defeat signalled
OL,7,Fthe end of an era for the trade union
OL,8,Fmovement. It preceded the
OL,9,Fnationalisation of more industries and
OL,10,Futilities, including steel, railways,
OL,11,Fgas and water.
OL,13,FOver the coming years dozens more pits
OL,14,Fshut and the industry was reduced to a
OL,15,Fshadow
OL,17,FKellingley Colliery in North
OL,18,FYorkshire, the UK's last deep coal
OL,19,Fmine, closed in December 2015.
