OL,6,FWhile many working in the industry
OL,7,Finsisted the mines had a future, Lord
OL,8,FHeseltine disputed the claim
OL,10,F"People will say that, but how many
OL,11,Fwere re-opened?" he said
OL,13,FHe added: "I don't think Arthur
OL,14,FScargill was a man with whom you
OL,15,Fcompromised."
OL,17,FAsked if he had been back to South
OL,18,FYorkshire since the pit closures, Lord
OL,19,FHeseltine was unsure.
